window.bookSummaryJSON = "Nicole Kraussâ€™ Great House was a finalist for the National Book Award. Her critically acclaimed debut novel <i>Man Walks Into a Room</i> follows Samson Greene, who, during the removal of a brain tumor, loses his adult memories. Feeling lost as an outsider in his own life, Samson agrees to participate in a scientific experiment in which memories are grafted from one brain to another."; 
